metadata.description: Multi-domain Q&A dataset combining technical, medical, financial, and general knowledge from real datasets, formatted for router LLM fine-tuning. Each domain targets 3000 examples. Each example contains "User query: [question]\nDomain: [domain]".

domains.technical: Programming and software development questions from OpenHermes, Dolly, Stack Exchange, Code Alpaca, and Stack Overflow datasets
domains.medical: Medical and health-related questions from PubMed QA and medical datasets
domains.financial: Financial and investment questions from financial QA datasets
domains.general: General knowledge questions from SQuAD and similar QA datasets
